{
  "page": "Love potion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/08/Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/400px-Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"283\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/08/Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/600px-Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/08/Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/800px-Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Love_potion_for_Egg_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Love potion for <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>, by Jota Saraiva ©</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Love potions</b> and <b>philtres</b> are concoctions believed to create feelings of love or attraction in the one who drinks it.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Love_potion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Mushroom\" title=\"Mushroom\">Mushroom</a> suggests that <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a> used love potions and philtres on Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a>, causing them to be rivals for her affections.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a> spit out a love potion put in his drink by Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhae_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhae Targaryen\">Rhae Targaryen</a>, who wanted her brother to marry her instead of their sibling, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Daella_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Daella Targaryen (daughter of Maekar I)\">Daella Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">Smallfolk</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> went to <a href=\"/index.php/Maggy_the_Frog\" title=\"Maggy the Frog\">Maggy the Frog</a> for fortunetelling, charms, cures, love potions, and the like.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Love_potion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Aegon</b>: And once my sister <a href=\"/index.php/Rhae_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhae Targaryen\">Rhae</a> put a love potion in my drink, so I'd marry her instead of my sister <a href=\"/index.php/Daella_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Daella Targaryen (daughter of Maekar I)\">Daella</a>.<br />\n</p><p><b>Duncan</b>: Did the potion work?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Aegon</b>: It would have, but I spit it out.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Love_potion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 19\">Chapter 19</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Cersei VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404213950\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 365/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8752/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2020/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 720/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2455/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.644      1 -total\n 70.31%    8.187      5 Template:Ref\n 37.84%    4.406      5 Template:Ref/core\n 20.30%    2.364      1 Template:References\n 14.49%    1.687      1 Template:Quote\n-->\n</d